Radio buttons are used when the user want to select the one among the group.
group them undee the same name.
we can Pre-select the radio button option and also we can disable the radio button option.
Code:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Radio Buttons Lab</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<!--code inside the 'wrapper' div -->
		<div id="wrapper">
			<input type = "radio" name = "radio" id="option1">
			<label>Male</label>
			<input type = "radio" name = "radio" id="option2" checked>
			<label>Female</label>
			<input type = "radio" name = "radio" id=option3 disabled>
			<label>Others</label>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
